<div class="survey-intro">
    <h2 class="survey-welcome">Welcome to our Survey on Social Media and Mental Health!</h2>
    <p class="survey-info-main">
        Thank you for participating in this important survey conducted by the Social Media Usage & Mental Health Committee. Your input is invaluable as we strive to understand the relationship between social media use and mental well-being in our community.
    </p>
    <h3 class="survey-title">About the Survey:</h3>
    <p class="survey-info">
        This survey aims to explore various aspects of social media usage and its potential impacts on mental health. Your honest responses will help us gather crucial insights into the experiences and challenges individuals face in the digital age.
    </p>
    <h3 class="survey-title">Your Privacy Matters:</h3>
    <p class="survey-info">
        We want to assure you that your participation in this survey is entirely anonymous. Your responses are confidential and will be aggregated for statistical analysis only. No identifiable information will be collected, ensuring complete privacy and confidentiality. 
    </p>
    <h3 class="survey-title">Why Your Input Is Essential:</h3>
    <p class="survey-info">
        Your perspective is crucial in shaping our understanding of how social media affects mental health. By sharing your experiences and thoughts, you contribute to a greater understanding of these issues, ultimately helping us create informed strategies for healthier digital engagement.
    </p>
    <p class="survey-info-end">
        Thank you for taking the time to share your thoughts and experiences with us. Let's work together to create a healthier and more mindful online community! 
    </p>

    <button class="survey-show">Take the Survey</button>
</div>

